==================
pytest-expect-test
==================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pytest-expect-test.svg
    :target: https://pypi.org/project/pytest-expect-test
    :alt: PyPI version

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/pytest-expect-test.svg
    :target: https://pypi.org/project/pytest-expect-test
